{"tid":1044730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【僵持3小時】中国漁船涉非法捕魚 遭阿根廷海警多輪開火追截","createTime":"2019-03-03T06:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T10:46:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0d66b00142dfafa81554f9128f3fe3c90cf905","tid":1044730,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"美聯社報道，阿根廷當地時間2日，海岸警衞隊對一艘中國漁船進行多輪開火。不過，開火是否擊中中國漁船、是否造成傷亡等情況，暫時還不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，按照阿根廷方面的說法，中國「華翔801」（音譯：Hua Xiang801）在阿根廷沿海水域非法捕魚。阿根廷海岸警衞隊發佈的影片顯示，他們向「華翔801」作出警告：「如果不撤退，他們就會開火。」在影片中，沒有聽到「華翔801」有回應，隨後阿根廷海岸警衞隊進行多輪射擊。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，事發在距離聖亞克灣358公里處的海域。阿根廷官員表示，在經過3小時僵持後，中國漁船撤回到國際水域。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190303/59324596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59324596&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=f33115d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59324596&h=7a834bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190303/59324596</a>"},{"pid":"a8ab39475df0306e69a3815f37c35547264a3de7","tid":1044730,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔擊沉佢?"},{"pid":"035f9501af9175658963a376d42bf3573a14ad5b","tid":1044730,"uid":987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"去到咁撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6ca257f61c075ce23d3b0576672d79da1a902f","tid":1044730,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"直接打沉佢啦"},{"pid":"759cbb0c32dd593bd375c18b176d149ca1316c3f","tid":1044730,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8ab39475df0306e69a3815f37c35547264a3de7","tid":1044730,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔擊沉佢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"因為油污都係污染自己海域，船上啲賤命都補唔返"},{"pid":"e4a0b598fcf179a3aecfdd0a91fd158580eceb2b","tid":1044730,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8ab39475df0306e69a3815f37c35547264a3de7","tid":1044730,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔擊沉佢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"瞄住駕駛倉打就ok"}]}